## rbloader project definition		-*- yaml -*-
name: rbloader
version: 0.0.1
summary: Load Ruby source files, reload when updated
description: RbLoader provides a 'load!' method with
  an interface generally similer to 'Kernel#require'.
  Under  'RBLoader::load!' any previouisly loaded Ruby 
  source file will  be loaded again, if updated since 
  previous 'load!'. The RbLoader class is defined under 
  the 'Utils' module.
